      "value": "<p>You fire a ray of freezing light from your weapon. You must be wielding a sword or spear to cast rage of halone. Make a spell attack roll. The ray deals 1d6 ice damage. If the target has the shadow trait, the ray deals an additional 1d6 holy damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The ray deals double damage.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The ray deals full damage.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The normal damage and damage to shadow creatures both increase by 1d6.</p>"
